    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064500/extras/972c170a95dfa6d254e13ccfdd4d7e17.avif?t=1771417328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064500/extras_big/972c170a95dfa6d254e13ccfdd4d7e17.webp?t=1771417328 width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064500/extras/9d4392f0895d08b6faeee43a5628dbb8.webp?t=1771417328\" alt=\"It&#039;s time to let the dogs out! Who? You!\" width=682 height=34 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bunch of crazy dogs are waiting for you to take them out to dominate the world! Well maybe not the whole world, but lets start with the park! Choose your favorite dog, create their own build with bizarre skills and design your own strategy to <strong>PEE</strong> all over the park and <strong>DESTROY</strong> your opponents. Become the alpha dog in this crazy fun action game with  <strong>MOBA</strong> and <strong>Battle Royale</strong> touches where only your skill will lead to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064500/extras/7c3fcb23dc4aa3c090a4a5cd668372d1.poster.avif?t=1771417328\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064500/extras/7c3fcb23dc4aa3c090a4a5cd668372d1.webm?t=1771417328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064500/extras/7c3fcb23dc4aa3c090a4a5cd668372d1.mp4?t=1771417328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DROP THE LEASH, IT’S TIME TO PEE</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Dogs with unique play styles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 <strong>Skills</strong> that you can mix and match to build your own strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 different ways to win the game: pee the territory to dominate it or eliminate your rivals. Choose yours or combine them both!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONE DOG TO RULE ‘EM ALL</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 cups and 16 arenas for your dogs to fight in</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 game modes with additional game mechanics for each arena.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Domination</strong>: The one who pees the most wins! Charge the fire hydrants to dominate de area, but watch out for the cars!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soccer</strong>: Join forces with other dogs and score a goal for your team.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle Royale</strong>: The tide is rising, there is no other choice but to fight before you drown!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race</strong>: Pick up the spawning <i>Chōchin</i> lanterns to gain a boost and splat all over the place.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DOMINATE WITH STYLE</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock customizables and new skins if you win the match!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 <strong>skins</strong> for each breed!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ <strong>customizables</strong> to equip your doggos with. Change their look &amp; personalise them exactly as you imagined!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thousands of skill combinations to choose from.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064500/extras/5042583126c9f6420114dcce97b57174.avif?t=1771417328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064500/extras_big/5042583126c9f6420114dcce97b57174.webp?t=1771417328 width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p>",
